OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,FBirthing services at Helme Chase at
OL,7,FWestmorland General Hospital will be
OL,8,Freinstated next year after services
OL,9,Fshut in May due to a shortage of
OL,10,Fmidwives.
OL,12,FAt the time, the University Hospitals
OL,13,Fof Morecambe Bay NHS Foundation Trust
OL,14,F(UHMBT) which runs the site said it
OL,15,Fwas because there was not enough staff
OL,16,Fto safely deliver care overnight and
OL,17,Fat weekends.
