OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,FSince the services were suspended, the
OL,7,FTrust says it has continued to recruit
OL,8,Fto vacant posts whilst also working
OL,9,Fwith maternity teams to review the way
OL,10,Fcommunity midwifery care is delivered
OL,11,Facross Morecambe Bay.
OL,13,FFrom February, women will be able to
OL,14,Fgive birth in the unit again supported
OL,15,Fby a midwife.
