OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,FSusan Foyle, Director of Midwifery,
OL,7,FUHMBT, said: "We are pleased to share
OL,8,Fthat a significant amount of midwifery
OL,9,Fvacancies have now been filled and a
OL,10,Fnew way of cross-bay working has been
OL,11,Festablished with our community
OL,12,Fmidwifery team which allows us to
OL,13,Fensure a sustainable service in the
OL,14,Fcommunity and at Helme Chase.
OL,16,F"This has enabled us to plan to
OL,17,Freinstate birth services at Helme
OL,18,FChase in February 2025."
