OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,FThe reinstated service at Helme Chase
OL,7,Fwill be provided by a cross-bay
OL,8,Fmidwifery team. To prepare for this,
OL,9,Ftraining and orientation will take
OL,10,Fplace during this month and throughout
OL,11,FJanuary.
OL,13,FFrom 6 January 2025, home births will
OL,14,Fbe available cross bay; and birthing
OL,15,Fservices at Helme Chase will be
OL,16,Frelaunched from Monday 10 February.
