OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,FHelme Chase will operate on the same
OL,7,Fmodel as it did before with women able
OL,8,Fto give birth in the unit 24-hours a
OL,9,Fday, seven days a week, supported by a
OL,10,Fmidwife (out of hours via an on-call
OL,11,Fsystem). Ante-natal and post-natal
OL,12,Fcare will continue as normal in the
OL,13,Funit.
