OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,FMs Foyle said: "As a Trust, we are
OL,7,Freally pleased that we are at the
OL,8,Fpoint where we can reinstate the
OL,9,Fservice at Helme Chase. We are fully
OL,10,Finvested in the NHS' plan for
OL,11,Fmaternity that advocates for
OL,12,Fpersonalised care and supporting women
OL,13,Fto give birth in a place of their
OL,14,Fchoice; and this allows us to deliver
OL,15,Fthat promise to our local communities.
