OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,F"I'd like to thank all the colleagues
OL,7,Finvolved for their professionalism and
OL,8,Fdedication to providing the best
OL,9,Fpossible care for women and families
OL,10,Facross Morecambe Bay. I'd also like to
OL,11,Fthank our local Maternity Voices
OL,12,FPartnership for their ongoing support
OL,13,Fand guidance."
OL,15,FJanet Gorry, Bay-Wide Maternity and
OL,16,FNeonatal Voices Partnership Lead,
OL,17,Fadded: "I am delighted that the
OL,18,Fmidwife-led birth services at Helme
OL,19,FChase are being relaunched, and 24
OL,20,Fhours home birth services will be
OL,21,Ffully available from January 2025.
