OL,3,CMaternity services to be reinstated at
OL,4,CCumbrian Hospital
OL,6,F"The dedication from midwives across
OL,7,FMorecambe Bay has been outstanding,
OL,8,Ftheir commitment to deliver safe and
OL,9,Feffective maternity care has ensured
OL,10,Fthe longer-term stability of Helme
OL,11,FChase for the community. I would like
OL,12,Fto take this opportunity to thank them
OL,13,Fon behalf of all the parents and new
OL,14,Fmums-to-be who have supported the
OL,15,Freopening of the midwife-led birth
OL,16,Fservices and home births across
OL,17,FMorecambe Bay."
